spec_data.Name: perl-Test-Object
spec_data.Description:
Test::Object is a testing package designed to allow you to easily test
what you believe is a valid object against the expected behaviour of
all of the classes in its inheritance tree in one single call.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 04:58:55 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Thoroughly testing objects via registered handlers
